    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loss 是一款 <strong>3D、第一人称、探索、谜题、动作、冒险和恐怖</strong> 游戏。你将扮演一位青少年男孩，某夜醒来后发现他的家人全都不见了。他们去了哪里？他为何会孤身一人？那些在房子里徘徊的奇异幽灵究竟是谁？在解开这个谜团的过程中，你将 <strong>探索你的房子、获取物品与钥匙、解锁门、解谜、寻找隐藏的笔记以及更多精彩内容！</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.poster.avif?t=1761557881\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.webm?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/8d345a0bbb5282e67c8a1e0b8d17a36d.mp4?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你遇到的生物同样相当凶猛，因此你必须展开反击！借助手电筒，你可以对准特定敌人几秒钟以将其击杀。这场刺激的战斗将始终让你保持紧张状态，并为较缓慢的解谜环节带来别样的节奏。 <strong>有多种武器以及各种类型的幽灵等待你去击败！</strong> 注意: 本游戏仅支持英语。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.poster.avif?t=1761557881\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.webm?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131240/extras/571c2c9560d3a81ce73315b149c070ca.mp4?t=1761557881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
